        Dear World
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sunset-earthwood">
        Fund With 25 is an initiative by <a
          href="https://www.example.com/hein-zin-thant-erik"
          class="text-blue-500 hover:text-sunset-mango hover:underline"
